verse.lines:
Dig deeper in those mysteries,
Let your seven locks grow long;
Oh anointing of Samson,
Let faith muscles become strong;
Lord, lead me to those pillars,
Let me cast those devils down,
Let me hear those Seven Thunders sound;
For the Spirit of Samson is on me,
Yes, the Spirit of the Lord is anointing me.

“Speak now my fair lady,
Touch the scepter in my hand;
Make known your desires
It’s my pleasure to command. ”
“Lord, my people, they are dying,
They must have their liberty;
Let me go and set the captive free. ”
For the Spirit of Esther is on me;
Yes, the Spirit of the Lord is
anointing me.
